name: AINN Rune Star
description: The AINN Rune Star is a spontaneous airdrop event launched by the AINN community on the eve of the Rune protocol's release, commemorating Satoshi Nakamoto's founding of Bitcoin. It marks the largest airdrop in history. The collection includes four tiers of rarity: 323 Satoshi Rune Stars, 5583 Rune Stars, 21000 Rune Star Cards and 183094 Rune Star Miners, designed to reward those original gangsters OGs who have made significant contributions to the Bitcoin ecosystem from multiple dimensions, including BRC20, NFTs, and AINN holdings.
